      <guid>http://shirtlah.com/singlish-alphabet/k-for-kaya/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;Kaya is coconut and pandan jam.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble speech right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Kaya plus butter plus toast bread is damn shiok, I tell you!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/div&gt;
  
    
    
    
    &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-speaker right&#34;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-inner&#34;&gt;
        
