&lt;h2 id=&#34;kaya-toast:7293f9a3068cac1db8c2903c86cea727&#34;&gt;Kaya Toast&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kaya toast is a staple breakfast item in Singapore,
and it&amp;rsquo;s super simple to make:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ingredients&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/alphabet/kaya-1.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;Kaya toast ingredients&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ingredients: butter, kaya, and a slice of bread.
You&amp;rsquo;ll also need a butter knife, and a toaster.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble speech right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Aburden! Liddat oso must say meh?&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/div&gt;
  
    
    
    
    &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-speaker right&#34;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-inner&#34;&gt;
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-image&#34;&gt;
            &lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/textbubble/limpeh-right-200x200.png&#34; /&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-name&#34;&gt;
            Limpeh
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  
  &lt;span class=&#34;clearfloats&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Butter first&amp;hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/alphabet/kaya-2.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;Kaya toast spread butter&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Toast the slice of bread, and while it is still hot,
spread a thick layer of butter on it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;hellip; then the kaya&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/alphabet/kaya-3.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;Kaya toast spread kaya&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Next a thin layer of kaya.
Do this quickly, before the butter melts into the bread,
so that the kaya and the butter mix - yum!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Best served with Milo/ Kopi/ Teh!&lt;/p&gt;

