    <item>
      <title>Shirt Lah! - Shirts for Singlish fans</title>
      <link>http://shirtlah.com/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Oct 2015 19:43:53 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://shirtlah.com/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Do you love to speak &lt;strong&gt;Singlish&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you find yourself &amp;ldquo;getting&amp;rdquo; jokes that only a Singlish speaker would get?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;re not the only one!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fact&lt;/strong&gt;: Pick an English joke/ pop-culture reference/ whatever,
and there&amp;rsquo;s a T-shirt somewhere out there, with that printed on it&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble speech right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Sure got wan!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;/div&gt;
  
    
    
    
    &lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-speaker right&#34;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-inner&#34;&gt;
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-image&#34;&gt;
            &lt;img src=&#34;http://shirtlah.com/images/textbubble/limpeh-right-200x200.png&#34; /&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
        
          &lt;div class=&#34;speaker-name&#34;&gt;
            Limpeh
          &lt;/div&gt;
        
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  
  &lt;span class=&#34;clearfloats&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; but Singlish on a T-shirt - now, that&amp;rsquo;s hard to find.
It&amp;rsquo;s like all the jokes went to a party together,
but the Singlish ones never got the invite.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;text-bubble-wrapper speaker&#34;&gt;
